{{en-noun|radars|-}}

# {{uncountable}} A method of [[detecting]] [[distant]] [[object]]s and [[determining]] their [[position]], [[velocity]], or other characteristics by [[analysis]] of sent [[radio]] [[wave]]s (usually microwaves) [[reflect]]ed from their [[surface]]s
